rows.label: tlk42100151_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I've never seen a Phonex that came
from Liberalitas.

rows.label: tlk42100151_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Since they come from a place with plenty to eat,
they must be plump Phonexes, right?

rows.label: tlk42100151_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I think they'd stand out, and I wouldn't forget if I saw one.
So, I'm sure I haven't.
